{"tid":872565,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人都會喺沖涼的同時洗埋頭同刷牙","createTime":"2018-10-22T20:11:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-22T20:30:36.000Z","uid":218083,"like":19,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4a1da37ce884f18be2a05e742fca942e3d73b6a8","tid":872565,"uid":218083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T20:11:42.000Z","msg":"是咁的 <br />\n之前同朋友仔講起點沖涼<br />\n小弟由細到大都會喺沖涼的同時洗埋頭同刷牙<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首先淋濕個頭同身<br />\n之後就用洗頭液同沖涼水查上去<br />\n然後左手一邊洗頭，右手拎住個牙刷狂刷<br />\n如果係早上出門口前沖嘅話<br />\n會同時去埋小便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n沖完抹番乾D水<br />\n就可以訓覺/出門口<br />\n全程都只係用左10幾分鐘就搞掂哂<br />\n乜咁樣沖法唔係幾好咩<br />\n<br />\n1.省時：同時做幾樣野，唔洗沖完先刷/洗頭<br />\n2.省水：用花灑一次過由頭淋到落尾，D水可以沖到頭同個身，打開個嘴就有得沖埋同口<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> =我都係咁做<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> =一向都分開做"},{"pid":"3622425ad6ab1ad56aea75cf2356671e142099a4","tid":872565,"uid":211528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T20:24:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"244df944fbe026024d62c1706dccf0bed75fd7dc","tid":872565,"uid":146728,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T20:28:45.000Z","msg":"你令我諗起去洗手盤洗撚個果post<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2421667a6254e760e60884e364bebe9ba093d668","tid":872565,"uid":160368,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T20:30:36.000Z","msg":"無你chur 到咁一邊刷牙一邊洗頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但日日都係沖住水黎刷牙"}]}